---
import { BellRingIcon, CheckCircleIcon } from "lucide-react";

---

<section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-20 lg:py-24 relative" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-display tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
            Your AI Workflow, Simplified
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">Set it up once, and watch the magic happen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-0">
        <div class="hidden md:block timeline-line z-0"></div>
        <div class="md:hidden absolute left-4 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/10 via-primary to-primary/10 z-0"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24 items-center">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1 flex justify-start md:justify-end">
                <div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl w-full max-w-md border-l-4 border-l-primary">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">
                            <BellRingIcon />
                        </span>
                        <span class="text-sm font-mono text-slate-400">Incoming Event</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-white font-medium">New 5-star review from Sarah J.</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">"The service was incredible, and the atmosphere..."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 size-8 bg-background-dark border-2 border-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-20">
                <span class="size-2.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 pl-8 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-display">01. Instant Detection</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">We monitor your Google Business Profile 24/7. As soon as a review lands, Automagic captures it instantly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24 items-center">
            <div class="order-1 md:order-1 pr-0 md:pr-8 text-left md:text-right pl-8 md:pl-0">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-display">02. Smart Processing</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Our AI analyzes sentiment and drafts a response based on your custom tone, keywords, and business rules.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 size-8 bg-background-dark border-2 border-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-20">
                <span class="size-2.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="order-2 md:order-2">
                <div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl w-full max-w-md relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider mb-2">
                            <span>AI Settings</span>
                            <span class="text-green-400 flex items-center gap-1"><span class="size-1.5 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></span>Active</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-card-dark/50 p-3 rounded border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Tone</span>
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">Professional &amp; Warm</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-card-dark/50 p-3 rounded border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Language</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Auto-detect (English)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-border-dark/50">
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1 font-mono">Drafting response...</div>
                            <div class="h-2 w-3/4 bg-slate-700/50 rounded animate-pulse mb-1"></div>
                            <div class="h-2 w-1/2 bg-slate-700/50 rounded animate-pulse"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1 flex justify-start md:justify-end">
                <div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl w-full max-w-md flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <div class="size-12 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                            <CheckCircleIcon />
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Response Published!</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">Google Maps â€¢ 12:42 PM</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 size-8 bg-background-dark border-2 border-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-20">
                <span class="size-2.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 pl-8 md:pl-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-display">03. Auto-Publish</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Set it to auto-pilot for 5-star reviews, or require approval for sensitive ones. The choice is yours.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>